original_title: 2006 - Sissel, Christmas with the Mormon Tabernacle Choir and Orchestra at Temple Square featuring Sissel
overview: European singing sensation Sissel joins with the Mormon Tabernacle Choir and Orchestra at Temple Square in a magnificent Christmas celebration featuring some of the season's most beloved songs. Recorded in high-definition, surround-sound stereo, Christmas with the Mormon Tabernacle Choir is a holiday tradition the entire family will enjoy.
tagline: Christmas with the Mormon Tabernacle Choir and Orchestra at Temple Square
title: 2006 - Sissel, Christmas with the Mormon Tabernacle Choir and Orchestra at Temple Square featuring Sissel
